@startuml
!include theme-white.puml
title AS-IS HUNTER Backend - Package Diagram

top to bottom direction

package "backend.main" as PMain
package "backend.api.routes" as PRoutes
package "backend.auth" as PAuth
package "backend.schemas" as PSchemas
package "backend.models" as PModels
package "backend.services" as PServices
package "backend.tasks" as PTasks
package "backend.integrations" as PIntegrations
package "backend.storage" as PStorage
package "backend.db" as PDb
package "backend.config" as PConfig

PMain ..> PRoutes : include_router()
PMain ..> PDb : engine / sessions
PMain ..> PModels : Base / User
PMain ..> PAuth : password bootstrap
PMain ..> PStorage : init_bucket()
PMain ..> PConfig : settings

PRoutes ..> PAuth : JWT + RBAC
PRoutes ..> PSchemas : request / response DTOs
PRoutes ..> PDb : AsyncSession dependency
PRoutes ..> PModels : ORM entities
PRoutes ..> PServices : business logic
PRoutes ..> PTasks : Celery dispatch
PRoutes ..> PIntegrations : direct connector calls
PRoutes ..> PStorage : presigned downloads

PAuth ..> PDb : current user lookup
PAuth ..> PModels : User
PAuth ..> PConfig : secret key / token TTL

PSchemas ..> PModels : enums / response mapping

PServices ..> PModels : domain entities
PServices ..> PIntegrations : external systems
PServices ..> PStorage : MinIO uploads
PServices ..> PDb : AsyncSessionLocal
PServices ..> PTasks : NLP helper import
PServices ..> PConfig : settings

PTasks ..> PServices : orchestration
PTasks ..> PDb : async sessions
PTasks ..> PModels : HuntingJob / IoC / Threat
PTasks ..> PConfig : Celery configuration

PIntegrations ..> PConfig : URLs / tokens / API keys
PIntegrations ..> PModels : IoC / enums

PStorage ..> PConfig : MinIO settings
PDb ..> PConfig : DATABASE_URL

note bottom of PServices
Main orchestration entry point:
backend.services.hunting_runner.run_hunting_job()
end note

@enduml
